        <h2>How to Use EcoRides ?</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>Go to the "Need a Ride" section.</li>
          <li>If you're not registered, click on the "Click Here" option to register.</li>
          <li>Book your ride and fill in all the necessary details. If there's someone with the same route, we'll notify you.</li>
