        <p>Requesting a ride is easy! Just follow these steps:</p>
        
        <ol>
          <li>Enter your <strong>First Name</strong> in the designated field.</li>
          <li>Specify the <strong>PickUp Point</strong> by typing in the address or location where you'll be starting your journey.</li>
          <li>Provide the <strong>Destination Point</strong> by entering the address or location of your final destination.</li>
          <li>Enter your <strong>Contact Number</strong> so that others can easily reach you for coordination.</li>
          <li>Share your <strong>Email</strong> address for any communication related to the ride.</li>
          <li>Indicate the <strong>Number of Persons</strong> traveling with you using the provided field.</li>
          <li>Choose the appropriate <strong>Vehicle Type</strong> from the dropdown menu. If none of the options apply, select "None".</li>
          <li>In the <strong>Additional Information</strong> textarea, you can provide any extra details you'd like to share with potential ride partners.</li>
